title: Bar & Baz & Shoop
info: Great coffee, delicious food and snacks, very reasonable prices. Railings outside to lock a bike to, covered by the station's CCTV, and stone floors inside so they don't mind cleats. Sofas are VERY comfortable - beware that you might not want to leave again!!
